M||tx|---
M||titl|Combine Multiple Array Iterations
M||impa|lo-md
M||impa|reduces iterations
M||tags|javascript, arrays, loops, perf
M||tx|---
M|Comb|tx|Multiple `.filter()` or `.map()` calls iterate the array multiple times. Combine into one loop.
M|Comb|**In|**
M|Comb|tx|```ts
M|Comb|tx|const admins = us.filter(u => u.isAdmin)
M|Comb|tx|const testers = us.filter(u => u.isTester)
M|Comb|tx|const inactive = us.filter(u => !u.isActive)
M|Comb|tx|```
M|Comb|**Co|**
M|Comb|tx|```ts
M|Comb|cons|us[] = []
M|Comb|cons|us[] = []
M|Comb|cons|us[] = []
M|Comb|tx|for (const us of us) {
M|Comb|tx|if (us.isAdmin) admins.push(us)
M|Comb|tx|if (us.isTester) testers.push(us)
M|Comb|tx|if (!us.isActive) inactive.push(us)
M|Comb|tx|}
M|Comb|tx|```